---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Shi Chen"
	description="Shi Chen is an undergraduate at UIUC studying Computer Science and Chemistry."
>
	<section class="profile-section">
		<img class="profile-photo" src="/profile.jpg" alt="Shi Chen" />
		<div class="profile-copy">
			<h1>Shi Chen</h1>
			<div class="contact-links">
				<span>shic4 [at] illinois [dot] edu</span>
				<span>/</span>
				<a href="https://github.com/Caesium135">GitHub</a>
			</div>
			<p class="bio">
				I am a Computer Science + Chemistry undergraduate @
				<a href="https://siebelschool.illinois.edu/">Siebel School Computing and Data Science</a>
				&
				<a href="https://scs.illinois.edu/">School of Chemical Sciences</a>
				of UIUC, interested in machine learning, scientific tools, and computational methods for
				experimental data.
			</p>
			<div class="experience-compact">
				<h2>Experience</h2>
				<div class="entry-list">
					<article class="entry-item">
						<div class="entry-heading">
							<h3>Murphy’s Group, University of Illinois</h3>
							<p>Feb 2025 – May 2026</p>
						</div>
						<p>
							Undergraduate Research Assistant working across both experimental and
							instrumental projects. Worked on synthesis, functionalization and
							characterization of AuNP, especially an individual project on cyanide etching
							upon 13nm AuNS with ligands of different surface charges such as MUA, MUO, and
							MUTAB. Assisted Siyu Zhou on Cu@AuNR for CO2 reduction catalysis, especially on
							data analysis and visualization for the publication. Built a website tool for
							rod sizing for the group with autonomous image processing and nanoparticle
							analysis on noisy TEM/STEM images through machine learning methods.
						</p>
					</article>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section-block" id="news">
		<h2>News</h2>
		<ul class="news-list">
			<li>
				<span class="news-date">Mar 2026</span>
				<p>
					Awarded the Thomas Remec and Susan Morisato Scholarship in Chemical Data
					Science, and excited to join
					<a href="https://thejacksonlab.github.io/">Jackson&apos;s Group</a>
					in Summer 2026.
				</p>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<section class="section-block" id="posts">
		<div class="section-header">
			<h2>Posts</h2>
			<a href="/posts">All posts</a>
		</div>
		<p class="empty-state">No posts yet.</p>
	</section>
</Layout>
